headline: Pinnacle West Sets Date for 2025 First-Quarter Financial Results, Webcast/Conference Call
summary: PHOENIX, April 01, 2025--Pinnacle West Capital plans to release its 2025 first-quarter financial results before the U.S. financial markets open on Thursday, May 1, 2025.
